Yes. This controller has quite a few branches worth covering.

## salesPoints()

You need tests for:

### 1. No cookie → redirect to auth

```java
@Test
void salesPoints_shouldRedirectToAuth_whenSessionIdMissing() {
    ModelAndView mv = controller.salesPoints("B2BOOST_BE", null);

    assertEquals("redirect:/auth/start?appId=B2BOOST_BE", mv.getViewName());
}
```

---

### 2. Blank cookie → redirect to auth

```java
@Test
void salesPoints_shouldRedirectToAuth_whenSessionIdBlank() {
    ModelAndView mv = controller.salesPoints("B2BOOST_BE", "");

    assertEquals("redirect:/auth/start?appId=B2BOOST_BE", mv.getViewName());
}
```

---

### 3. Session not found

```java
@Test
void salesPoints_shouldRedirectToAuth_whenSessionNotFound() {

    when(redisSessionService.findBySessionId("session-123"))
            .thenReturn(null);

    ModelAndView mv =
            controller.salesPoints("B2BOOST_BE", "session-123");

    assertEquals("redirect:/auth/start?appId=B2BOOST_BE",
            mv.getViewName());
}
```

---

### 4. No sales points

```java
@Test
void salesPoints_shouldRedirectToNoSalesPoint_whenNoSalesPoints() {

    UserSession session = new UserSession();
    session.setSalesPoints(Collections.emptyList());

    when(redisSessionService.findBySessionId("session-123"))
            .thenReturn(session);

    ModelAndView mv =
            controller.salesPoints("B2BOOST_BE", "session-123");

    assertEquals("redirect:/error/no-sales-point",
            mv.getViewName());
}
```

---

### 5. Success path

```java
@Test
void salesPoints_shouldReturnSalesPointsView() {

    UserSession session = new UserSession();

    SalesPoint sp = new SalesPoint();
    sp.setId("SP001");

    session.setSalesPoints(List.of(sp));

    when(redisSessionService.findBySessionId("session-123"))
            .thenReturn(session);

    ModelAndView mv =
            controller.salesPoints("B2BOOST_BE", "session-123");

    assertEquals("views/sales-points", mv.getViewName());

    assertEquals(
            session.getSalesPoints(),
            mv.getModel().get("salesPoints"));

    assertEquals(
            "B2BOOST_BE",
            mv.getModel().get("appId"));
}
```

---

### 6. Exception path

```java
@Test
void salesPoints_shouldRedirectToTechnicalError_whenExceptionOccurs() {

    when(redisSessionService.findBySessionId("session-123"))
            .thenThrow(new RuntimeException("boom"));

    ModelAndView mv =
            controller.salesPoints("B2BOOST_BE", "session-123");

    assertEquals(
            "redirect:/error/technical",
            mv.getViewName());
}
```

