---

### 9. Success path

```java
@Test
void selectSalesPoint_shouldRedirectToPartner() {

    when(authService.completeSalesPointSelection(
            "session-123",
            "SP001"))
            .thenReturn("https://partner.example.com");

    ModelAndView mv =
            controller.selectSalesPoint(
                    "B2BOOST_BE",
                    "session-123",
                    "SP001");

    assertEquals(
            "redirect:https://partner.example.com",
            mv.getViewName());
}
```

---

### 10. Exception path

```java
@Test
void selectSalesPoint_shouldRedirectToTechnicalError_whenExceptionOccurs() {

    when(authService.completeSalesPointSelection(
            anyString(),
            anyString()))
            .thenThrow(new RuntimeException("boom"));

    ModelAndView mv =
            controller.selectSalesPoint(
                    "B2BOOST_BE",
                    "session-123",
                    "SP001");

    assertEquals(
            "redirect:/error/technical",
            mv.getViewName());
}
```

